- Suppression list synchronization with SendGrid (periodic or event-driven).

6) Contact / Support Form (Public & Authenticated)
- Page: page_006, page_004, page_005, page_015, page_027 align with ROAM design system.
- Public contact form:
  - Fields: name, email, subject, message, category (General, Concierge, Billing, Technical).
  - Basic anti-spam (honeypot, reCAPTCHA v3 optional).
  - Optional newsletter opt-in.
  - On submit: create a support/inquiry record, trigger an acknowledgment email, and notify concierge/admin as needed.
