  - Authenticated: GET/PUT /api/support/:id, POST /api/support/:id/messages
  - Admin: GET /api/support/export (CSV), GET /api/support/:id
- Payments
  - POST /api/payments/link (generate/send payment link)
  - GET /api/payments/receipts/:id (retrieve receipt)

10) Integration Touchpoints
