- Security:
  - JWT-based auth or existing session mechanism; role-based access control for admin endpoints.
  - Validate inputs server-side; use CSRF protection for form submissions where applicable.
  - Ensure unsubscribe endpoints properly disable sending to that address.
- Validation:
  - Input validation on all forms; server-side and client-side.
  - Substitution schema validation for templates; ensure required keys exist for each template version.

